<font color=#FFFF00><i>Clear.</i></font>

135
00:09:53,509 --> 00:09:55,078
<font color=#FFFF00>02:52.</font>

136
00:09:56,145 --> 00:09:58,014
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasien meninggal.</font>

137
00:09:58,815 --> 00:10:00,817
<font color=#FFFF00>Panggil walinya.
/ Baik.</font>

138
00:10:14,464 --> 00:10:17,967
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jika bukan begitu, itu tentang ibumu?</i></font>

139
00:10:18,368 --> 00:10:20,837
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Karena aku tidak bisa menyelamatkannya?</i></font>

140
00:10:22,605 --> 00:10:24,240
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bukankah sudah jelas?</i></font>

141
00:10:25,375 --> 00:10:27,076
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jika kau ada di posisiku...,</i></font>

142
00:10:27,977 --> 00:10:31,247
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...bisakah kau tidak membenciku?</i></font>

143
00:11:12,488 --> 00:11:14,257
<font color=#FFFF00>Oke, ini cukup.</font>

144
00:11:27,236 --> 00:11:29,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini? Kenapa dia berdarah?</font>

145
00:11:30,707 --> 00:11:32,408
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu kau, bukan dia.</font>

146
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:37,513
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bersandar.
Darah bisa memblokir saluran napasmu.</font>

147
00:11:37,513 --> 00:11:38,981
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingin tercekik?</font>

148
00:11:39,115 --> 00:11:41,117
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dokter bedah tidak tahu itu?</font>

149
00:12:18,154 --> 00:12:19,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau baik-baik saja?</font>

150
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:21,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak akan.</font>

151
00:12:23,326 --> 00:12:26,696
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mau apa?
/ Ikut aku.</font>

152
00:12:29,766 --> 00:12:31,634
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mau apa?</font>

153
00:12:31,634 --> 00:12:34,437
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu Ayah tidak punya belas kasihan...,</font>

154
00:12:34,437 --> 00:12:36,739
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi ini keterlaluan.</font>

155
00:12:37,507 --> 00:12:40,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa dia menyusahkan
seorang dokter begitu sering?</font>

156
00:12:40,610 --> 00:12:41,744
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.</font>

157
00:12:44,714 --> 00:12:46,816
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Kim.
/ 15 menit.</font>

158
00:12:47,083 --> 00:12:49,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Selama itulah siklusnya berlangsung.</font>

159
00:12:57,126 --> 00:12:59,896
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejak hari kedatangan ibuku sampai hari ini...,</font>

160
00:13:00,463 --> 00:13:02,565
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau tidak mengambil cuti.</font>

161
00:13:02,765 --> 00:13:05,334
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan hari ini, kau bahkan
melakukan operasi yang sulit.</font>

162
00:13:05,334 --> 00:13:07,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau bekerja keras tanpa istirahat...,</font>

163
00:13:07,370 --> 00:13:11,741
<font color=#FFFF00>...bahkan pria sehat pun akan
pingsan karena kelelahan.</font>

164
00:13:12,208 --> 00:13:14,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Kosongkan pikiranmu...,</font>

165
00:13:14,110 --> 00:13:17,246
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan hanya 15 menit, biarkan...</font>

166
00:13:27,156 --> 00:13:28,758
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah beristirahat.</font>

167
00:14:34,357 --> 00:14:35,625
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ke sini.</font>

168
00:14:37,493 --> 00:14:39,328
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari ini, apakah...</font>

169
00:14:42,231 --> 00:14:43,566
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa Ayah terbangun?</font>

170
00:14:45,468 --> 00:14:49,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sedang mengerjakan sesuatu.</font>

171
00:14:51,974 --> 00:14:53,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu?</font>

172
00:14:53,142 --> 00:14:55,978
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mendapatkannya dalam surat hari ini.</font>

173
00:14:56,746 --> 00:14:59,015
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini dari Dokter Song Eun Jae.</font>

174
00:15:10,026 --> 00:15:11,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah akan menjawabnya?</font>

175
00:15:13,229 --> 00:15:14,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebisa mungkin.</font>

176
00:15:34,250 --> 00:15:35,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Song...</font>

177
00:15:37,586 --> 00:15:39,755
<font color=#FFFF00>...selalu membawamu kembali padaku.</font>

178
00:15:43,059 --> 00:15:44,193
<font color=#FFFF00>Tetapi aku...</font>

179
00:15:45,695 --> 00:15:47,396
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengambil ibunya...</font>

180
00:15:49,598 --> 00:15:50,967
<font color=#FFFF00>...dari dia.</font>

181
00:15:54,437 --> 00:15:56,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi aku tidak boleh menyerah.</font>

182
00:16:00,576 --> 00:16:02,144
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak boleh.</font>

