<font color=#FFFF00>Kita punya pasien lain.
/ Tolong beri jalan.</font>

344
00:27:56,058 --> 00:27:58,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku  mendapat telepon.
Aku mencari Song Woo Jae.</font>

345
